text:
https://httpd.apache.org/docs/current/mod/mod_proxy_hcheck.html seems misleading.  It notes it is to be used for balancer members, but then provides examples for non balancer members, for example

ProxyHCExpr ok234 {%{REQUEST_STATUS} =~ /^[234]/}
ProxyPass "/apps"     "http://backend.example.com/" hcexpr=ok234
